1. *Ludilo* se nastavlja danima i noćima. (The madness continues day and night.)
2. Ona je u potpunosti pala u *ludilo*. (She completely fell into madness.)
3. On je bio preduhitren njegovim *ludilom*. (He was overwhelmed by his madness.)
4. Oni su pokušali da spreče njegovo *ludilo*. (They tried to prevent his madness.)
5. Oni su izgubili razum u *ludilu*. (They lost their mind in madness.)